# ğŸ§  Productivity Dashboard

A Fully all-in-one **Productivity Dashboard** built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
It combines a **Todo List**, **Pomodoro Timer**, **Motivational Quotes**, **Daily Planner**, and **Goal Tracker** to help you stay organized and motivated throughout your day.

