### ğŸ“… Daily Planner
- Time-blocked planner from 9 AM to 5 PM
- Save tasks for each hour using localStorage
- User-friendly input fields and save buttons

### â± Pomodoro Timer
- 25-minute timer with start/reset functionality
- Built-in productivity technique to boost focus
- Plays an alarm sound on completion

### ğŸ’¡ Motivational Quotes
- Random quote displayed every page load
- Encourages positive mindset and consistency

### ğŸ¯ Daily Goals Tracker
- Tick off up to 5 goals every day
- Simple checkbox UI to track personal progress

### ğŸ•’ Live Clock & Date
- Displays the current day, date, and time
- Auto-updates every second

